title: Plant Based News talks to à-bas-le-ciel
description: Will Klaus Mitchell and Eisel Mazard ever patch it up?  No, probably not.  BTW, I'd like to make a video (ASAP) talking about the absurd feud between Gary Francione and Melanie Joy… this is a recurrent feature within veganism, at all levels, and in all categories… although, as you'll hear in this recording, I do reach out positively to other youtubers in general, and I reached out positively to Klaus, specifically, even in a tense situation such as this: Klaus did make a video (that he has now deleted) in which he referred to my court case as "a scam", backing up lies that were then created by Durianrider and Vegan Cheetah.
